msgid "Following the walls"
msgstr "Longer les murs"

#. type: Content of: <p>
#: src/lessons/maze/WallFollowerMaze.html:3
msgid ""
"This time, the maze is a bit more complicated. Random won't be enough, we "
"ough to be smart!"
